metadata.description:
Meet Catwoman. She's addicted to the night. And addicted to Batman. But most of all, Catwoman is addicted to danger. She can't help herself, and the truth is--she doesn't want to. She's good at being bad, and very bad at being good. The feline fatale headlines her own self-titled series!

This series is rated Teen+.
metadata.name: Catwoman
